titles.title: To repeal section 10(f) of Public Law 93-531, commonly known as the "Bennett Freeze".

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Natural Resources.

bill.summary:
2/8/2007--Introduced.
Amends federal law to repeal the requirement regarding the freeze on the development of lands in litigation under the Navajo-Hopi Settlement Act of 1974.
